headline: Micron (MU): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: Micron has been on fire lately. In the past six months alone, the company’s stock price has rocketed 179%, setting a new 52-week high of $219.50 per share. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
